The onX Detailed Weather Alarm notifies the user of the weather forecast of their current location every day at a specified time. It provides a detailed forecast, and when the notification is clicked, the accuweather website is opened showing an in depth forecast for the current location.

Files:
onXweather0_1.onx.js
index.php*

*index.php of onxweather.t15.org, the temporary work-around to reverse geocode the location and provide a usable address for accuweather.

